Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃…吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样他一下子就会沦陷的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  上吧月水木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御同学  你可不能让女孩子害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同意  你要用绅士的态度去面对她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软软的  看上去很甜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOOD JOB
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御同学你真是太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
